pony express is a 1926 american western film directed by james cruze and written by john k. butler . the film stars william boyd , andy clyde , rand brooks , john miljan , william elmer , john miljan , william elmer , jr. , forrest tucker , john miljan , john miljan , william elmer , jr. , forrest tucker , and william shatner . the film was released on december 1 , 1926 , by paramount pictures .